  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "chapterTitle": "与认知偏差“友好相处” 试着怀疑“我没问题”",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300098005_8_564-635",
          "range": "564-635",
          "rangeStart": 564,
          "rangeEnd": 635,
          "markText": "①了解人类共同的思维习惯；②站在自己和他人两种角度思考，注意到双方在认知上的差别；③面临重要抉择时，不要急着做出判断，养成搜集确切信息的习惯。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1718759842,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-19 09:17:22",
          "chapterUid": 8,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=564&rangeEnd=635",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=564&rangeEnd=635"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_11_2260-2297",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2260-2297",
      "markText": "有时，在他人的诱导下，我们会身临其境般地“想起”实际上并没有发生过的事情。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2260&rangeEnd=2297",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2260&rangeEnd=2297"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_6_638-672",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "638-672",
      "markText": "认知偏差是大脑为了减轻信息处理的负担选择“走捷径”而发生的“故障”。",
      "totalCount": 600,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=638&rangeEnd=672",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=638&rangeEnd=672"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_3_902-993",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "902-993",
      "markText": "认知偏差中的“认知”指的是记忆、选择、判断等与人类思维相关的心理活动，“偏差”意味着歪曲、失真。因此，认知偏差的意思是“思维上的偏颇”，即先入为主、偏见等，它们都是人类下意识的反应。",
      "totalCount": 544,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=902&rangeEnd=993",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=902&rangeEnd=993"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_8_606-635",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "606-635",
      "markText": "面临重要抉择时，不要急着做出判断，养成搜集确切信息的习惯。",
      "totalCount": 465,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=606&rangeEnd=635",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=606&rangeEnd=635"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_11_1582-1669",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "1582-1669",
      "markText": "大脑不会原封不动地记录我们的所见所闻，有时候，对于实际上没有经历过的事情，我们却坚信自己真实地经历过，这就是“虚假记忆”。",
      "totalCount": 462,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1669",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=1582&rangeEnd=1669"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_5_574-637",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "574-637",
      "markText": "“我看问题还是很客观的”“我总是理性思考”，诸如此类都是认知偏差。有的人认为“我肯定没问题”，但这种想法本身就是一种认知偏差。",
      "totalCount": 425,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=574&rangeEnd=637",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=574&rangeEnd=637"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_11_2954-3116",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2954-3116",
      "markText": "除了诱导之外，我们在反复想象某事的过程中，有时候会无法区分自己的想象与实际的经历，这种现象叫作“想象膨胀”。",
      "totalCount": 396,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2954&rangeEnd=3116",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2954&rangeEnd=3116"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_12_1869-1960",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1869-1960",
      "markText": "举个例子，心情舒畅时，我们会对未来的前进道路充满期待和希望，对遇到的人抱有良好的印象，经常关注积极信息；反之，颓唐消沉时，我们会对前途感到悲观，对他人抱有负面印象，容易关注消极信息。",
      "totalCount": 336,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1869&rangeEnd=1960",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1869&rangeEnd=1960"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_10_1066-1118",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "1066-1118",
      "markText": "人类的记忆中隐藏着多种多样的认知偏差，这是因为人类会根据自己的偏好或事情的结果更改记忆，美化过去的事情，",
      "totalCount": 319,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1066&rangeEnd=1118",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=1066&rangeEnd=1118"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_17_2893-3136",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "2893-3136",
      "markText": "与有名效应类似的认知偏差还有“单纯接触效应”，它指的是在与同一事物反复接触的过程中，对该事物的喜欢程度逐渐提高。",
      "totalCount": 315,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2893&rangeEnd=3136",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=2893&rangeEnd=3136"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_19_2860-2917",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2860-2917",
      "markText": "社会学中的“标签理论”指出，越轨行为并非是由人的内在因素导致的，而是与周围环境中的社会成员给他贴上的标签密切相关。",
      "totalCount": 289,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2860&rangeEnd=2917",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2860&rangeEnd=2917"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_15_2593-2603",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2593-2603",
      "markText": "未做之事最易让人后悔",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2593&rangeEnd=2603",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2593&rangeEnd=2603"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_38_1235-1612",
      "chapterUid": 38,
      "range": "1235-1612",
      "markText": "人们倾向于认为自己所属的群体（内群体）的成员具有多样性，而与自己无关的群体（外群体）的成员具有较强的同质性，“他们都一个样子”，这叫作“外群体同质性效应”。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1235&rangeEnd=1612",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=38&rangeStart=1235&rangeEnd=1612"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_16_1332-1383",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "1332-1383",
      "markText": "我们倾向于在事情发生之后，感觉自己在知道结果之前就已经预测到了，这叫作“事后聪明偏差”。",
      "totalCount": 286,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1332&rangeEnd=1383",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=1332&rangeEnd=1383"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_6_494-510",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "494-510",
      "markText": "为了轻松一点，大脑选择“走捷径”",
      "totalCount": 280,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=510",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=494&rangeEnd=510"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_7_575-611",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "575-611",
      "markText": "在某些事情上，认知偏差可以让你屏蔽沮丧不安的情绪，促进自我肯定感的提升。",
      "totalCount": 266,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=611",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=575&rangeEnd=611"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_5_498-512",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "498-512",
      "markText": "“我没问题”就是一种主观臆断",
      "totalCount": 247,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=498&rangeEnd=512",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=498&rangeEnd=512"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_32_1773-1855",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "1773-1855",
      "markText": "无法按时完成计划而遭遇失败的经历数不胜数，但在制订新的计划时，仍然认为自己“能按计划进行”，这叫作“规划谬误”。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1773&rangeEnd=1855",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=1773&rangeEnd=1855"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_52_1946-1998",
      "chapterUid": 52,
      "range": "1946-1998",
      "markText": "当改变有利有弊的时候，比起做出改变，人们更愿意维持现状不变，这种现象叫作“维持现状偏差”。",
      "totalCount": 238,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1946&rangeEnd=1998",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=52&rangeStart=1946&rangeEnd=1998"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300098005_19_1577-1645",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1577-1645",
      "markText": "给信息加上特定的“标签”，促使人们朝着某个方向理解或记忆事物，这叫作“标签效应”。它可以塑造事物的形象，将标签与事物之间的联系固定下来。",
      "totalCount": 230,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300098005&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1577&rangeEnd=1645",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/6b532940813ab8cc8g015d3c?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1577&rangeEnd=1645"
    }
  ],
